      "id": "",
      "questionNumber": 139,
      "questionText": "<p>Match List <b>I</b> with List <b>II</b>:</p>\n<style type=\"text/css\">\n.tg  {border-collapse:collapse;border-spacing:0;}\n.tg td{border-color:black;border-style:solid;border-width:1px;font-family:Arial, sans-serif;font-size:14px;\n  overflow:hidden;padding:10px 5px;word-break:normal;}\n.tg th{border-color:black;border-style:solid;border-width:1px;font-family:Arial, sans-serif;font-size:14px;\n  font-weight:normal;overflow:hidden;padding:10px 5px;word-break:normal;}\n.tg .tg-c3ow{border-color:inherit;text-align:center;vertical-align:top}\n.tg .tg-0pky{border-color:inherit;text-align:left;vertical-align:top}\n</style>\n<table class=\"tg\">\n<thead>\n  <tr>\n    <th class=\"tg-c3ow\" colspan=\"2\"> List I (Mixture) </th>\n    <th class=\"tg-0pky\" colspan=\"2\"> List II (Separation Technique) </th>\n  </tr>\n</thead>\n<tbody>\n  <tr>\n    <td class=\"tg-0pky\">A.</td>\n    <td class=\"tg-0pky\">$\\mathrm{CHCl}_3+\\mathrm{C}_6 \\mathrm{H}_5 \\mathrm{NH}_2$</td>\n    <td class=\"tg-0pky\">I.</td>\n    <td class=\"tg-0pky\">Steam distillation</td>\n  </tr>\n  <tr>\n    <td class=\"tg-0pky\">B.</td>\n    <td class=\"tg-0pky\">$\\mathrm{C}_6 \\mathrm{H}_{14}+\\mathrm{C}_5 \\mathrm{H}_{12}$</td>\n    <td class=\"tg-0pky\">II.</td>\n    <td class=\"tg-0pky\">Differential extraction</td>\n  </tr>\n  <tr>\n    <td class=\"tg-0pky\">C.</td>\n    <td class=\"tg-0pky\">$\\mathrm{C}_6 \\mathrm{H}_5 \\mathrm{NH}_2+\\mathrm{H}_2 \\mathrm{O}$</td>\n    <td class=\"tg-0pky\">III.</td>\n    <td class=\"tg-0pky\">Distillation</td>\n  </tr>\n  <tr>\n    <td class=\"tg-0pky\">D.</td>\n    <td class=\"tg-0pky\">$\\text { Organic compound in } \\mathrm{H}_2 \\mathrm{O}$</td>\n    <td class=\"tg-0pky\">IV.</td>\n    <td class=\"tg-0pky\">Fractional distillation</td>\n  </tr>\n</tbody>\n</table>",
